Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Comment: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP end}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio came to an elegant ball—in name only—and got surrounded by deeply jealous women,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then accidentally broke her vow of abstinence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Shinobu and Onijima
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,fought to decide who'd get to sacrifice himself to save the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at the ball, Benio once again \Nbrought chaos in her special fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,With the High Collar Lady around, no event is safe from ending in a grand brawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Serving as a decoy, \NShinobu went on a one-man assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,His selfless act moved Onijima, \Nwho has now regained consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and is desperately calling out to him to no avail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander! Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're still alive, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:09.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF2EAF7&\blur1.001\bord0\pos(734.8,150.4)}Episode 30 \N{\fs70.001}Shinobu's Final Battle in Scattered Petals! {花と散る少尉の最後!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:13.59,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs100.001\blur1.001\bord0\c&HF3E8E6&\pos(697.65,351.33)}Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go! All-out assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you?! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now, Akechi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All-out assault! Kyaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again, boys of the detective club...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come. Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I must avenge the commander by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Onijima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Onijima, so you've also made it out alive after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dead sure there was \Nno hope for you, Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone! \NThe deputy commander is safe too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe and that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. When I left you to rest in that trench \Nand attacked the enemy by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd never get to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Platoon commander! Deputy commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come to your rescue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried for you and me, \Nthe entire platoon rushed to our rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Kobayashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, you're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy commander! We might be hopeless good-for-nothings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but we'll stick together unto death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right, boys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've decided to entrust our lives to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll follow you to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I can't let you die in vain.\NI'll do whatever it takes to protect all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, your change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, it sure has turned chaotic.\NAnd it's all because Benio showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As always... \NI am nothing but a burden on Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is doing her best to become more ladylike, but I led her astray...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you love Benio that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. But, Ranmaru, you have to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio loves Shinobu now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing how excited she is when she receives Shinobu's letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,how impatiently she waits for his return...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I, on the other hand... \Ncan't help but chase hopelessly after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I know full well that she'll never turn back for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep trying to satisfy \Nmy unquenchable thirst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Even if my love \Nwill never be reciprocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you may think of me \Nas an idiot for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pure child. What a pure child you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, you need to come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make sure to return home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, we won't have any outlet for our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see them, Second Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We are... deep into enemy territory, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we defend this place to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, have you picked up kendo again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope I'll never have to face you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting all that feminine just isn't in my nature, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My shoulders got stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should stop forcing myself. \NI am who I am, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said! That's the Benio we all know and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, how about we practice together again? \NFor old times' sake, Ranmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Th-Thanks, but I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Ushigorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! I've just remembered that I have an urgent matter to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How dull. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, you haven't sent me any letters lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I've heard from you was when you got sent to the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I shouldn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised that you'd return home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me that you {\i1}will{\i0} return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy seems to be drawing closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounded like a 70mm howitzer, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become quite used to explosions, haven't you, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been on the front line for two months, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How does a toast sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I still find it strange that someone like you ended up in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We are an infamous unit\Ncomposed entirely of outcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only a matter of time before we got sent to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you must have left \Na lot behind back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,First from Tokyo to Kokura and now to Russia. \NThey've been harsh to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a pretty girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so. \NYou got any pictures of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, lemme see what she's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A pug-nosed girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flesh, she's nothing like this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's irascible and quick to fly off the handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But deep down, she's kind, magnanimous, indomitable, and has a strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd never leave someone in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander,\Nwhy {\i1}did{\i0} you get sent all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home soon, okay? Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather and Grandmother don't seem to have any appetite at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Receiving no news from Young Master must have cast a gloom over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's possible for them to enjoy their meal at times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer it if they had \Nat least a slice of bread, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A slice of bread, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, one two. \NOne, two, one two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We absolutely gotta let them win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, I told you we're not allowed to win!{previously: mustn't, which is somewhat British. I'm not 100% confident this is the more natural alternative}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're crying \Nat the sight of some anpans?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It reminded me of Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes back over twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master had lost his appetite \Nbecause of a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so I brought him some anpans to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From that moment onward, \Nwe had our little secret
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:14:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would make anpans \Nfrom time to time only for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, this is our entire ration for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Crackers from emergency rations?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi, do we really have to use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We don't have a single grain of rice left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, the others haven't made any complaints about food,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but we definitely won't last long like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware. In normal circumstances, we would've been resupplied two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't heard anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, there was a large formation of cossacks surrounding our position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's move out of here. \N We'll evacuate and run to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Second Lieutenant, we were ordered to defend this place to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to move! Leave everything you don't need behind. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't we been sent any provisions in three days?\NHeadquarters is to blame for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up! \NWe'll soon reach headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I can see the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one last push, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight we'll finally fill our stomachs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no lookouts stationed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No flags flying, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, there's nobody here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's left, not a living soul here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:54.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2F4CDE&\b0\bord1.001\3c&HD8DFD5&\fs20\frz305.8\pos(244.59,772.45)}(Top Secret)                                                      \h\N{\fs\c&H0B1C35&}Siberia Invasion Plans {guess}
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.52,0:16:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Those high command \Nbastards stranded us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, they've used us, burdens that we are, as a decoy for their retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what you'd expect! Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't even send us any supplies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone. In a situation like this, the best we can do is save our own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll break out of the encirclement \Nand try to rejoin with the rest of the division.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do this by running through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only ally is the dark of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well: forget about defeating the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for your life, just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not fighting for the fate of Japan here.\NThis is just an intervention war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't let ourselves get killed in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fighting to survive and return home. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, the same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to survive to return to your Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Platoon, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! My leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did everyone make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, Sergeant Onijima is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Onijima?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you guys can leave without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave Onijima behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this! \NYou'll face certain death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll return to Japan all together. \NGet moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Onijima! Where are you, Onijima?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Onijima!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't come here! \NLeave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so reckless?\NYou'll just end up dying too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Onijima!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Comman⸺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,White... White petals of Malinka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}White... White Malinka...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The symbol of Shinobu's safe return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting... I'll be waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu's portrait cracked...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me something bad happened to him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Commander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you \Nthat you must return to your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander! Why... \NWhy did you sacrifice yourself for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.92,0:22:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The snow falls on the Siberian landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as Sergeant Onijima, moved by Shinobu's sacrifice, sheds manly tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment Benio is notified of his death in battle, \Nthere'll surely be no end to her tears. {/will cry tears of blood}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:55.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 31 of {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady:{\i0} \N"No Tears Left to Cry" {ああ涙もかれ果てて}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu's promise to return home safely is broken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,once Benio is informed of his tragic death in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The grief obstructs her throat to the point she can no longer wail
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and clogs her eyes \Nto the point where she has no tears left.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Her love for Shinobu pours out of her heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and her intense feelings form a tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See in the next episode of {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"No Tears Left to Cry." {ああ涙もかれ果てて}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:20.90,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 31 \NNo Tears Left to Cry {ああ涙もかれ果てて}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Comment: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED start}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
